<div><h3>GAME 160 - Foley and Field Recording </h3>  <hr>This course involves the research and production of audio recordings using live studio-based Foley techniques and site-based field recordings. The class will involve the use of microphones, portable recorders, studio recording, location-based recording, and advanced digital editing tools to develop audio assets such as sound effects for interactive media and video.<br><br><strong>Anticipated Terms Offered:</strong> Spring<br><br></div>		</td>
